oe14-reagent-name-basic-empty = Empty solution
oe14-reagent-desc-basic-empty = Natural solvent. Essentially a useless liquid that dilutes useful effects. Getting rid of it will give you much more concentrated solutions.

oe14-reagent-name-basic-heal-brute = Healing solution
oe14-reagent-desc-basic-heal-brute = Can heal all types of physical damage.

oe14-reagent-name-basic-damage-brute = Ulcer solution
oe14-reagent-desc-basic-damage-brute = If ingested, causes flesh eating and other mechanical injuries.

oe14-reagent-name-basic-damage-heat = Incendiary solution
oe14-reagent-desc-basic-damage-heat = Causes severe fire burns and even sets fire.

oe14-reagent-name-basic-heal-heat = Soothing Solution
oe14-reagent-desc-basic-heal-heat = Capable of healing most burns.

oe14-reagent-name-basic-heal-cold = Warming Solution
oe14-reagent-desc-basic-heal-cold = Capable of healing even serious frostbite.

oe14-reagent-name-basic-damage-cold = Ice solution
oe14-reagent-desc-basic-damage-cold = Dangerous substance that causes severe frostbite.

oe14-reagent-name-basic-heal-poison = Antidote solution
oe14-reagent-desc-basic-heal-poison = An effective antidote used for treating most common poisons.

oe14-reagent-name-basic-damage-poison = Poisonous solution
oe14-reagent-desc-basic-damage-poison = Capable of causing extreme indigestion, ulcers, intoxication, and in sufficient dosage to cause death.

oe14-reagent-name-basic-damage-airloss = Asphyxiating Solution
oe14-reagent-desc-basic-damage-airloss =  A viscous slurry that rapidly glues the victim's insides together, causing severe shortness of breath.

oe14-reagent-name-basic-heal-airloss = Air solution
oe14-reagent-desc-basic-heal-airloss = A refreshing liquid that saturates the body with air.

oe14-reagent-name-basic-damage-manadepletion = Mana-depleting solution
oe14-reagent-desc-basic-damage-manadepletion =  A dangerous solution that damages areas with mana inside the body.

oe14-reagent-name-basic-heal-manadepletion = Mana-healing solution
oe14-reagent-desc-basic-heal-manadepletion = A liquid that affects the mana within the body, revitalising areas dried up by mana.

oe14-reagent-name-basic-blood-restore = Blood-healing solution
oe14-reagent-desc-basic-blood-restore = Coming into contact with the body restores blood levels of the same type used by that body.

oe14-reagent-name-basic-blood-absorption = Blood-absorbing solution
oe14-reagent-desc-basic-blood-absorption = A liquid that burns blood in the body. An extremely dangerous substance that can cause long-term sickness.

oe14-reagent-name-basic-satiate-hunger = Saturating solution
oe14-reagent-desc-basic-satiate-hunger = A mixture that effectively restores hunger.

oe14-reagent-name-basic-satiate-thirst = Life-giving moisture
oe14-reagent-desc-basic-satiate-thirst = A liquid that tastes very much like water. It tastes strange, but it's a good thirst quencher.

oe14-reagent-name-basic-heal-mana = Liquid mana solution
oe14-reagent-desc-basic-heal-mana = A substance that causes a rapid regeneration of magical energy in the body.

oe14-reagent-name-basic-damage-mana = Antimagic solution
oe14-reagent-desc-basic-damage-mana = A substance that rapidly drains all magical energy from the body.

oe14-reagent-name-basic-heal-stam = Refreshing solution
oe14-reagent-desc-basic-heal-stam = A substance that causes a rapid regeneration of stamina in the body.

oe14-reagent-name-basic-damage-stam = Exhausting solution
oe14-reagent-desc-basic-damage-stam = A substance that rapidly drains all stamina from the body.

oe14-reagent-name-basic-speed-up = Accelerating solution
oe14-reagent-desc-basic-speed-up = Increases muscle tone, allowing creatures to move and react faster than normal.

oe14-reagent-name-basic-speed-down = Slowing solution
oe14-reagent-desc-basic-speed-down = Makes you think and move slower.

oe14-reagent-name-see-rainbow = Hallucinogenic solution
oe14-reagent-desc-see-rainbow = Causes cheerful hallucinations, colors the whole world in rainbow bright colors.

oe14-reagent-name-basic-emote-cough =  Coughing solution
oe14-reagent-desc-basic-emote-cough = Coughs profusely, but harmlessly.

oe14-reagent-name-basic-vomit = Vomit solution
oe14-reagent-desc-basic-vomit = A substance that causes severe vomiting spasms. May help with food poisoning.

oe14-reagent-name-basic-drunk = Booze solution
oe14-reagent-desc-basic-drunk = A substance that causes dizziness and slurred speech.

oe14-reagent-name-basic-jitter = Jitter solution
oe14-reagent-desc-basic-jitter = A substance that causes uncontrollable but safe spasms throughout the body.

oe14-reagent-name-basic-sleep = Sleeping solution
oe14-reagent-desc-basic-sleep = Dangerous substance, even in small doses, that sends you to sleep.

oe14-reagent-name-basic-unsleep = Awakening solution
oe14-reagent-desc-basic-unsleep = A substance that stimulates the body and instantly brings it out of any sleep.

oe14-reagent-name-basic-confuse-aura = Aura concealment solution
oe14-reagent-desc-basic-confuse-aura = A substance that temporarily alters your magical aura.